# Privacy Policy

F Prompt does not collect, transmit, sell, or share user personal data.

The extension stores user preferences and favorite prompts locally in the browser using Chrome storage. This data remains on the user's device and is not uploaded to any server.

The extension only runs on supported ChatGPT pages to display the prompt gallery and insert prompts selected by the user. It does not read, collect, or upload chat history, account information, passwords, or personal messages.

F Prompt does not use analytics, advertising trackers, or third-party data collection services.
